result: No many people have the courage to walk through The Spook Garden.
Trees as old as the night, and a thick stench passing through those that dare to come here, shivering them like ghosts.
What keeps everyone out is The Jacked o' Lantern.
Leave if you value your life.
Because no one who enters can leave The Spook Garden.
You've brought me down. This won't happen again.
So you have ten seconds to leave before I bask in The Spook Garden and heal up like this fight never happened.
